title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim update 14 beta - new build available
description:
In this video we will look at what has been added and what has been fixed in the 4rdbeta release for Sim Update 14 which will be released in a few weeks. The fix list contains several fixes mainly for cockpits as well as some aircrafts. This build also contains the V2 version of the Airbus A320.
